print(" - Node Charlie (Mesh-IP: 200::3): 8GB RAM, 4 Cores (Idle)")
print(" - Node Delta (Mesh-IP: 200::4): 32GB RAM, 16 Cores (Idle)")

print("\n[Solomon] Total Pooled Resources: 64GB Unified RAM, 32 Unified CPU Cores.")
